{"tid":594006,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樂視體育fb發帖向觀眾道別","createTime":"2018-03-15T12:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T13:33:21.000Z","uid":1886,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"90a3944fdf231c8fd386a48131da993f51935617","tid":594006,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"樂視體育香港於fb發文，管理員以「別了」為題，暗示該公司「今天完場」。帖文稱，一眾前線與後援行政的同作人員，盡力工作最後一刻，形容這些經驗不是金錢可以換取，也非筆墨所能形容。該公司又呼籲觀眾，要繼續支持本地體育、以至評述及主播工作者。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2030000/2030961/letv_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2030000%2F2030961%2Fletv_1024.jpg&h=42ffdcf9&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2030961/%E6%A8%82%E8%A6%96%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2fb%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%96%E5%90%91%E8%A7%80%E7%9C%BE%E9%81%93%E5%88%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2030961%2F%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%25A6%2596%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2fb%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B8%2596%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25A7%2580%25E7%259C%25BE%25E9%2581%2593%25E5%2588%25A5&d=HJ3VHFVOi4atUZKNgWQtTKEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=8e37f729\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2030961/%E6%A8%82%E8%A6%96%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2fb%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%96%E5%90%91%E8%A7%80%E7%9C%BE%E9%81%93%E5%88%A5</a>"},{"pid":"11f845872d4a310c72a11bccc9d9020aeff7b98e","tid":594006,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T12:43:53.000Z","msg":"樂視體育擁有英超及美國NBA播映權，但早前遭兩間公司入稟，申請清盤。樂視體育的荃灣辦公室，今日（15日）下午仍有員工進出，但多名員工均封口，不願談論及透露公司情況。消委會今早表示，過去曾多次聯絡樂視體育卻不成功。"},{"pid":"b0904b7b4867d85ff6330449355ebee2eec8f715","tid":594006,"uid":56533,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T12:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5sE9RU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fup